    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Scapulars of cloak-style or small scapulars worn by Christian penitents, typically under clothing; they may be made of rough wool and decorated with the crucifix and instruments of the Passion.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
